        "subject": "LU-6241 ldiskfs: missing ldiskfs patch for SLES11 SP3",
        "message": "LU-6241 ldiskfs: missing ldiskfs patch for SLES11 SP3\n\nSLES11 SP3 is missing the ext4-export-64bit-name-hash\npatch which prevents osd-ldiskfs from building on that\nplatform. The simple fix is to include the needed\nldiskfs patch.\n\nChange-Id: Ie672e18bbabb8a082e38d82c94be46fa6179b6c9\nSigned-off-by: James Simmons <uja.ornl@gmail.com>\n"
      },
